{{> header title="Activate your eSIM"}}

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Your eSIM is ready to activate</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Hi %%NAME%%,
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Your service is now ready to use, so you should activate as soon as possible.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Order number:<br /></strong>%%ORDER_NUMBER%%
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Plan name:</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          %%PLAN%%
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>{{brand.displayName}} mobile number:</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          %%MOBILE_NUMBER%%
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>How to activate your eSIM</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <ol style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Remember your mobile number<br /></strong>You'll need your new {{brand.displayName}} mobile number, so make a note of it before continuing. <br /></li>
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 16px;"><strong>Get the {{brand.app.name}} app</strong><br />Download the {{brand.app.name}} app on the eSIM-enabled phone you want to use your new plan on.
              <br /><br />
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                  <td style="border-radius: 4px; background-color: {{brand.colors.primary}};">
                    <a href="{{brand.oneAppUrl}}" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 30px; display: inline-block;">Get the {{brand.app.name}} app</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </li>
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Activate a new eSIM<br /></strong>Open the {{brand.app.name}} app, select “Activate a new eSIM” and follow the prompts. For more information, check out our %%ESIM_SUPPORT_PAGE%%.<br /></li>
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Need to transfer an existing mobile number to us?<br /></strong>After activating, call us on {{brand.support.phone}} and we’ll help you transfer your number to us. Do not delete your eSIM profile in the meantime as it will stop your transfer. Your old SIM will stop working once your transfer is complete.<strong><br /></strong></li>
          </ol>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px 60px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}};">
          Thanks,<br>
          Your {{brand.displayName}} Team
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

{{> footer}}
